<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.6.2">
<l>cilampaṭi yuruviṉ karuneṭuṅ kaṇṇār</l>
<l>tiṟattaṉā yaṟattaiyē maṟantu</l>
<l>pulampaṭin tuṇṇum pōkamē perukkip</l>
<l>pōkkiṉēṉ poḻutiṉai vāḷā</l>
<l>yalampuri taṭakkai yāyaṉē māyā</l>
<l>vāṉavark karacaṉē vāṉōr</l>
<l>nalampurin tiṟaiñcun tiruvaṭi yaṭaintēṉ</l>
<l>naimicā raṇiyat tuḷentāy.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Being a man [always] at the side of ladies with dark, long eyes</l>
<l rend="indent">and the beauty of ankleted feet,</l>
<l>Neglecting virtue, multiplying pleasures</l>
<l rend="indent">to which the senses succumb and enjoy,</l>
<l>I spent much time in vain! Herder whose broad hands bear the plough</l>
<l rend="indent">and conch, dark [lord], king of celestials,</l>
<l>I took refuge at the divine feet where celestials bow,</l>
<l rend="indent">longing for [your] goodness, my father in Naimiśāraṇyam.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
